-- 15 Business Problems & Solutions

1.Count the number of movies and tv shows
2.Find the most common rating for movies and tv shows
3.List all the movies released in a particular year (e.g., 2020)
4.Find the top 5 countries with most content on netflix and split countries if multiple countries are listed
5.Identify the longest movie available on netflix
6.Find content added in the last 5 years
7.Find all the movies / tv shows directed by a specific director (e.g., "rajiv chilaka")
8.List all the tv shows with more than 5 seasons
9.Find each year and the average number of content released by india on netflix and return top 5 years with highest average content released
10.List all movies that are documentaries
11.Find all content without a  director listed
12.Find how many movies actor "salman khan" appears in last 10 years
13.Categorize the content based on the presence of the keywords 'kill' and 'violence' in the description field. Label content 
   containing these keywords as 'Bad' and all other content as 'Good'. Count how many items fall into each category
14.List 20 random titles (quick sample)
15.Using REGEXP to find titles that start with a number
